law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491, effective March 19, 1977. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 62, sec. 24. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 133, sec. 2. -- Amended 1944 Ky. Acts ch. 35, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 971-6, 971-7.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Special judge by agreement if regular judge absent or cannot preside, or office is vacant. -- Designation of special judge by chief justice of Supreme Court.
